      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of picture caption in Sept 13 article about winemaking in Virginia</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture caption in this section last Wednesday with an article about winemaking in Virginia referred incompletely to a house designed by Thomas Jefferson on the grounds of what is now Barboursville Vineyards. The picture showed the house when it was still standing; as the article noted, it is now a picturesque ruin.</p>
      </block>
